            <fr:blockquote><fr:p>We are excited to share the news of the Lean Focused Research Organization (FRO)! A new nonprofit dedicated to advancing the Formal Mathematics revolution, we aim to tackle the challenges of scalability, usability, and proof automation in the <fr:link href="jms-019G.xml" title="Lean" addr="jms-019G" type="local">Lean proof assistant</fr:link>. Our 5-year mission is to empower <fr:link href="jms-019G.xml" title="Lean" addr="jms-019G" type="local">Lean</fr:link> towards self-sustainability</fr:p>
